snippet.title: Namco Museum Collection 2 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Captured off the OG Evercade Handheld.
NOTE: This cart is NOT compatible with the Evercade VS. It only works with the OG Evercade and the Evercade EXP.

Games in this cart:
00:00:08 - Burning Force (MegaDrive / Genesis)
00:03:38 - Dig Dug II (Famicom)
00:08:14 - Dragon Spirit: The New Legend (Famicom)
00:13:46 - Galaga (Famicom)
00:16:20 - Pac-Attack (SNES)
00:29:45 - Phelios (MegaDrive / Genesis)
00:34:06 - Splatterhouse 3 (MegaDrive / Genesis)
00:46:00 - Splatterhouse Part 2
00:52:07 - The Tower of Druaga (Famicom)
00:55:50 - Warpman (Famicom)
00:59:55 - WeaponLord (SNES)
